description: `GtpuSupervisionProfile`: This table stores GTPU supervision profile configurations for different cells, specifying parameters like echo settings and interface association.  Columns: `dateTime` (timestamp of record), `Area_Name` (geographic area), `CellId` (cell unique identifier), `Id2` (duplicate of CellId?), `Id3` (unknown identifier), `Id4` (interface type, possibly S1/X2), `vsDataType` (data type identifier), `vsDataFormatVersion` (data format version), `GtpuSupervisionProfile.userLabel` (user-defined label), `GtpuSupervisionProfile.gtpuEchoDscp` (DiffServ Code Point for GTPU echo), `GtpuSupervisionProfile.gtpuSupervisionProfileId` (profile ID, possibly S1/X2), `GtpuSupervisionProfile.gtpuEchoEnabled` (echo enabled status), `GtpuSupervisionProfile.interfaceList` (list of interfaces), `GtpuSupervisionProfile.endpointResourceRef` (reference to endpoint resource).
